Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.29,0:27:25.33,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,ぼく\N
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.29,0:27:25.33,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,なに\N
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.33,0:27:28.46,Rubi-ja,,0,0,0,,ことば\N
Dialogue: 0,0:27:25.33,0:27:28.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,解かるよ\N
